    "era_2": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "h2b": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "The Tom Era — 1997–2025",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "heading_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "t2b": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Tom Huber's Legacy.</strong> In the late '90s, Tom Huber took over and spent nearly three decades building one of the most diverse card and collectible inventories in the region. His love for the hobby turned the shop into a time capsule. Tom's presence, generosity, and passion made it more than a store — it was a part of the community's fabric.</p>",
            "text_size": "t2"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["h2b", "t2b"],
      "settings": {
